name: Queen of HeN
description: Any bitch can spend a mans money, ride in his car, lay in his house, order off the menu and spread her legs. But only a real woman can help a man achieve his goals in life, yeah that's me, support him when hes broke, push him to be successful, shower him with positive energy, compliment him on a regular basis and never kick him while hes down. That's me, Ben's wife, pok..pokk.poookk...im real chicken.
